  <brief_title>A Study to Look at Antiepileptic Drug Levels While on Lamictal or Depakote With or Without an Oral Contraceptive</brief_title>
  <official_title>Variation of Serum Valproate and Lamotrigine Levels in Relation to The Menstrual Cycle and Oral Contraceptive Use</official_title>
